      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i was cutting veggies and the knife slipped, i got a pretty deep cut on my forearm. it’s still kind of oozing blood even though i’ve been pressing on it. i dont really want to go to the hospital if i dont have to, do u think i can just put some organic honey on it and bandage it up? i heard that helps things heal faster",
